<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<manifest xmlns:android="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android" android:versionCode="11" android:versionName="1.1.5" package="net.bluetoothviewer.full">
	<uses-sdk android:minSdkVersion="14" android:targetSdkVersion="19" />
	<uses-permission android:name="android.permission.BLUETOOTH" />
	<uses-permission android:name="android.permission.BLUETOOTH_ADMIN" />
	<application android:theme="@android:style/Theme.Holo" android:label="Bluetooth Viewer" android:icon="res/drawable-ldpi-v4/launcher_main.png" android:name="net.bluetoothviewer.application.BluetoothViewerFullApplication" android:allowBackup="true">
		<activity android:name="net.bluetoothviewer.BluetoothViewer" android:windowSoftInputMode="0x2">
			<intent-filter>
				<action android:name="android.intent.action.MAIN" />
				<category android:name="android.intent.category.LAUNCHER" />
			</intent-filter>
		</activity>
		<activity android:theme="@android:style/Theme.Dialog" android:label="Select a device to connect to" android:name="net.bluetoothviewer.DeviceListActivity" android:configChanges="0xa0" />
		<activity android:theme="@android:style/Theme.Dialog" android:label="Settings" android:name="net.bluetoothviewer.SettingsActivity" android:configChanges="0xa0" />
	</application>
</manifest>
